Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為 提到椎名真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天才畫家…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你才是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}入浴場景好像不夠撩情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}綾乃她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 是在說漫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別…別對著臉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打濕的臉相當耐人尋味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在的我就那麼嫵媚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大致上了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 了解什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 你要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回房間 繼續畫原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這蓮蓬頭就這麼放著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新人獎的截稿日期快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就不能從正面回答一下我的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夠了 回房間去加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}油？油炸豆腐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要加油的是誰啊
