Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:25.04,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,350)\bord1\shad0\blur3\fs45\c&HFFFFFF&}於是，你想問什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:25.04,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,350)\bord1\blur3\shad0\fs45\c&HFFFFFF&}不﹑沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:25.04,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,350)\bord1\blur3\shad0\fs45\c&HFFFFFF&}這樣啊，那我先下囉
