Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:41.75,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs60\shad0\c&H5E78D4&\pos(796,183)}招\N募\N飼\N主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:41.75,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\shad0\c&H8D816E&\frz0.7063\pos(632,113)}詳\N情\N請\N諮\N詢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}招募飼主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於想搬出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼終於啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分我一些 我去對面幫你貼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想幫忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山碰到什麼好事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}碰到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飼主的事情我去幫你問問游泳部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼快就找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然找到了一個想養貓的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想做貓的飼主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}需要飼主的是你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神 神田同學 飼主是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛剛那個是指找個人來照顧還沒習慣日本高中生活的椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又 又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.62,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}※也有陪我一下的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛤？這麼乾脆就告白了 這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}星期天有個想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼嘛 原來是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}約…約會？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我為了幫貓找飼主 很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去拜託仁學長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶 神田同學 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼好不好的 這與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟了 糟了 糟了 大事不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 學弟也趕快換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你你你拉到我的內褲啦 脫掉的話會有奇怪的東西蹦出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我非常介意 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是誰的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難得的星期天在吵什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白和仁去約會了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就約個會而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說是要去情人旅館啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}情 情情人旅館？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種情人做那事專用的旅館 簡稱作情人旅館？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 就是那個情人旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白被NTR了你也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她只是去給漫畫取材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有必要鬧這麼大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是那個後宮王仁學長去旅館卻什麼都不做 這種事可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三鷹的話肯定會出手的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和新幹線到站時間記錄的精準度一樣毋庸置疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 換好衣服在門口集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}60秒內到達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}30秒內過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今晚要吃紅豆飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:24.30,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur5}※日本人在遇到喜事的時候會吃紅豆飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用找錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}稍…稍微等等 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太慢了 學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}限制解除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}解開手上的負重物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我… 這是… 在做什麼修行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經…盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明明還能再變身三次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才說地球人太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你果然是外星人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢著 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反應很近 謹慎點前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}跟蹤也請交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 反應來自哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}距離真白大人還有10公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 這看起來像是在取材嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看起來像在約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是因為學弟太馬虎大意才會這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這個軟弱的傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這個軟弱的傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼說了兩遍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 我已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}住手 不會讓你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我去讓我去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍不住了 滿溢的思念就快要漏出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}萬一暴露了該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶然撞見戰術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這戰術太膚淺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在做什麼啊 神田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為為…為什麼青山會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為週日聲優培訓完之後在這裡打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還是這麼厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 七海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你穿制服的樣子也很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來來 我們一起躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事 上井草學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 神田同學你靠得太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得哪個好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個比較可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 同感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是生日禮物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給一個近在咫尺 卻遙不可及的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 請給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像買了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 我該回店裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}休息時間已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦…加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算神田同學不這麼說我也會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美咲學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 我胸口好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種病 會傳染的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好像也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算照顧椎名的不是我也無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁學長是喜歡漂亮乖巧型的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最早開始交往的風香也是這種類型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從那時起就開始跟蹤他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用跟蹤我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼在仁身邊的總不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會真的要進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐 不趕快阻止他們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道說是膝枕？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至少表現出痛的表情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就不要說！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說這麼輕易就讓人枕在你的大腿上 你到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}關於地球的事情之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尺度太大啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 仁學長呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他說「跟計劃一樣 之後空太會照顧你的」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛤？和計劃一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道說 跟蹤的事暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 給我等等 你明白現在的狀況了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}情人旅館裡面 孤男寡女啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道 今天要住這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說你完全沒弄明白吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽好了 椎名 你做事前要多考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟男人一起來這種地方 萬一發生了什麼事的話該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}考慮了也沒有意義 我是來取材的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了畫漫畫 這是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我才到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明說了很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經找到貓的飼主了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有弄明白的人 是空太吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「你迄今為止是怎麼過的」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「畫了畫」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「一直畫到現在」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 本來是打算讓你打一拳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一不小心我就條件反射性的出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}OL的留美小姐的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今晚請回櫻花莊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夠了 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經看不下去了 美咲學姐那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唉…還是說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼美咲學姐就不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是看到了她消沉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我肯定會忍不住想推倒她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在問你 真白怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名她已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在你的懷中？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一個人睡在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夾在鞋櫃和牆壁之間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈哈哈…你在搞什麼呢 和她吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連架都沒能吵成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}單方面吃了致命的連招然後就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之前什麼都沒想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名真的是太過於與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的常識完全不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是對椎名來說 那些都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有畫畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在應該是畫漫畫吧 對她而言才是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的是沒有一點迷茫 總之很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天真白說了 來日本就是為了成為漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說「難得在海外得到了認可 這樣不是很可惜嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「那種東西我不需要」她這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是個了不得的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 多虧了椎名 我清醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要自己決定自己的歸所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會把送別會搞得很盛大的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會很期待的
Comment: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.13,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:26.82,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}過ぎるだけの  時間じゃ悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:26.82,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一味流逝的時光 徒增懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:29.86,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}刻まなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:29.61,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}唯有銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:35.96,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}「此処にいる」と心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:35.87,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}「我就在這裡」 內心如此吶喊的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.37,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.37,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:45.00,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}迷いながら  涙を飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:45.00,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不斷迷茫著 逞強噙住眼角淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:51.46,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不器用だね　夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:51.22,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真是笨拙呢 連夢想都不斷繞道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:57.22,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大空を見上げ　何も見えず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:57.39,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}仰望這片廣闊的天空 卻無法確認一物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:22:05.52,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}胸が痛むわけ考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:22:05.65,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也曾思考過內心會如此疼痛的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:07.05,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}DAYS  of  DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.05,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.90,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}風を走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.99,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}飛奔而出 風聲過耳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:16.31,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君と僕の中で　何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:16.31,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在你與我的內心中 究竟有什麼開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.41,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}わからないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.47,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}雖然沒有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:26.09,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}キラキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:26.00,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但是就朝著炫目陽光照耀的地方一直前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:31.88,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}永遠など　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:31.88,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}雖然無法知道 何謂永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}關於昨天的事 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說的沒錯 沒弄明白的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要你跟我說 下次我一定會陪你的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新人獎 要加…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要離開櫻花莊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？我內褲的顏色…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:39.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fs43\b1\blur3\pos(710,450)}色彩斑斕的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變態！你在問什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想像也不可以！
